---
title: Lemon-Pepper Double Pork and Braised Potatoes with Feta Aioli
description: Tonight's Mediterranean-style supper is a twist on classic Greek lemon potatoes. Instead of getting slow-roasted in a lemon broth, they're braised in a pan on the stove!
